<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<title>Marvel Studio</title>
<style>
body {
background-image: url("https://wallpaperaccess.com/full/1868188.jpg");
background-attachment: fixed;
background-position: center;
background-repeat: no-repeat;
background-size: cover;
}
#marvel_studio {
height: 500px;
position: absolute;
top: 50%;
left: 50%;
margin-right: -50%;
transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
width:60%;
}
#Title {
width: 100%;
background-color:red;
padding:3px;
}
#TitleName {
text-align: center;
color: white;
}
#Content {
opacity: 0.8;
background-color:black;
height: 100%;
}
#ContentHead {
color:white;
height:100px;
width:100%;
display:inline;
text-align:center;
font-weight:bold;
}
#popularHeros {
width: 50%;
float: left;
}
#popularVillains {
width: 50%;
float: right;
}
#ContentBody {
width:100%;
display:inline;
text-align:center;
}
#Heros {
width: 50%;
float: left;
}
#Villains {
width: 50%;
float: right;
}
div.images {
text-align:center;
margin: 2px;
width:100px;
padding-left:10px;
padding-bottom:15px;
display:inline-block;
}
div p {
text-align: center;
color:black;
background-color:white;
margin:0px;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div id="marvel_studio">
